<L>__{exterior shaolin temple day}
<B>__{establishing shot of d.s. as he walks along the path.}
<A>__{in the b.g. can be seen drew, li, wu and a couple other of the disciples. they are waiting for something. the d.s. hits the trip wire and suddenly two bamboo poles hurtle towards him, ready to slam him in the shoulders. with one beautiful move, the d.s. breaks both poles, shattering when they hit his arms. the d.s. hardly breaks stride and continues walking. he looks back once, and sees the outline of the group of disciples.}
<B>__{angle on drew and the guys}
<A>__{who are up and running as soon as they are spotted. they run by gao, who was watching from another area.}
